<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/vnext/schema/core/profile/link> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "\n  A web page or other resource related to the subject.\n  "@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/vnext/schema/core/profile/link> <http://schema.org/domainIncludes> <https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/vnext/schema/core/profile/ProfileCredential> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/vnext/schema/core/profile/link> <http://schema.org/rangeIncludes> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
